{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回\"生不如死\"讲述了田思思在王大娘地牢中的恐怖经历。她遇到被折磨毁容的女孩子，得知王大娘的残忍手段。后被奇奇（外表如猩猩的可怜人）所救，但奇奇因痴情而被田思思利用并杀害。葛先生多次出现威胁逼婚，田思思在恐惧中逃亡。最终遇到好心的老头子搭车，却在喜宴上发现新郎倌竟是葛先生，陷入更深的绝望。本章展现了田思思从天真少女开始面对江湖险恶的成长过程。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "受过很大刺激",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王大娘要我问你一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她要你……问我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她要我问你，你想不想变成我这样子?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你怎会变成这样子的?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是已经肯答应了?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不知道……我不知道……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道就是答应了，你本该答应的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不说话了?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的话已说完。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不想法子逃走?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定有法子的，你不能这样等死!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不想走，我宁可死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中原孟尝",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道爹爹竟要我嫁给他?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这样子跑出去，岂非要笑死人么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么晚了，田二爷何必走呢?不如就在这里歇下吧?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，我有急事，要去找个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他忽然长叹了口气，接着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不必怕我，我是来救你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你来救我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那条绳子是你放下去的?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了我还有谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么要救我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你很可爱，我很喜欢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚!滚开些，只要你碰一碰我，我就死!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怕我?为什么怕我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我长得虽丑，却并不是坏人，而且真的对你没有恶意，只不过想……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想怎么样?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你叫做什么名字?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇奇，我叫奇奇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇奇",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你究竟是不是人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎么样害你的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "格格",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他抬头，望着田思思，目中又充满乞怜之意。道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你恨不恨她?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然恨她，为什么不想法子杀了她?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你怕她。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她不是人……她才真的是个野兽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然这么怕她，为什么敢救我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "奇奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为……冈为我喜欢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若真的对我好，就该替我去杀了她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算你不敢去杀她，至少也该放我走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，你一个人无论如何都休想逃得了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我可以帮你逃出去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "奇奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽是个人，但不像别的人那样，会说假话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我也不能一个人走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "奇奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还有个妹妹，我不能抛下她在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她是个怎么样的人?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "奇奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我去找她——我一定可以救她出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "奇奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你会不会走?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不会的，我等着你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人难道会魔法?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他淡淡地接着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不能这么样做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我偏要这么样做，你有什么法子阻止我?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噗",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若真的不愿嫁给他，我倒有个法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么法子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀了他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀了他?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁也不能勉强将你嫁给个死人的，是不是?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我能杀他?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当然能，因为他喜欢你，所以你就能杀他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你只有在爱上一个女人的时候，她才能伤害你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他慢慢地接着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "它为什么叫女人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他现在已经快回来了，是嫁给他，还是杀了他，都随便你，我绝不勉强……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "田心呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "奇奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我找不到她，因为……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么要杀我?……我做错了什么?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的确应该杀我的，我不怪你……我不怪你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不怪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不怪你……我不怪你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哧",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道刚才他随时都能杀你的?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的声音仿佛很遥远，慢慢地接着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回去吧，客人都已去了，王大娘正在等着你，快回去!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王大娘",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不回去。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不回去怎么行呢?你难道还要我抱着你回去?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你，让我走吧……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_jie",
      "speaker_name": "梅姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你走不了的，既已来到这里，无论谁都走不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当真的想走，我倒也有个法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么法子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你答应我一件事，我就让你走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "答应你什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "答应嫁给我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "葛先生这一定是在开玩笑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的认为我是在开玩笑?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算葛先生答应，我也不能答应的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我就只好杀了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是王大娘……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王大娘",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我答应你!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你等我?为什么等我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有句话要问你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什……什么话?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你打算什么时候嫁给我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我要嫁给你?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自己说的，你已经答应了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有说，我没有答应……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一天我究竟做了些什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我做的究竟是什么事?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我究竟能算是个怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这就是人生?难道这不是人生?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道一个人非得这么样活着不可?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "田小姐，田小姐……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们想来干什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 876,
      "line_end": 876
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还敢来找我?胆子倒真不小。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都已知道错了么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 898,
      "line_end": 898
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小人们知错，小人们该死……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 900,
      "line_end": 900
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 904,
      "line_end": 904
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你来干什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 934,
      "line_end": 934
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我来问你一句话。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 936,
      "line_end": 936
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "问什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 938,
      "line_end": 938
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你打算什么时候嫁给我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 940,
      "line_end": 940
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这四个人是我叫他们来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 950,
      "line_end": 950
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 952,
      "line_end": 952
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "东西他们既已还给你，你为什么不要?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 954,
      "line_end": 954
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不要，我什么都不要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 956,
      "line_end": 956
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他收起包袱，又慢慢地接着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 962,
      "line_end": 962
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "葛先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你一定要嫁给我，你答应过我的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 970,
      "line_end": 970
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有答应你……我真的没有答应你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 982,
      "line_end": 982
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知姑娘要到哪里去?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1022,
      "line_end": 1022
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "田心这小鬼不知道是不是真的逃了。她本事倒比我还大些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1034,
      "line_end": 1034
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘你莫非遇着了强盗么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1048,
      "line_end": 1048
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个大姑娘家，本不该单身在外面走的，这年头人心已大变了，什么样的坏人都有……唉!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1052,
      "line_end": 1052
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的家远得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1056,
      "line_end": 1056
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "远得很，有多远?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1058,
      "line_end": 1058
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在江南。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1060,
      "line_end": 1060
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南，那可就没法子送，怎么办呢?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1062,
      "line_end": 1062
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知老爷子你本来要到哪里去?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1064,
      "line_end": 1064
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我呢?我到什么时候才有这一天?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1110,
      "line_end": 1110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘你想到哪里去呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1118,
      "line_end": 1118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叮叮当当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1136,
      "line_end": 1136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那怎么好意思呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1140,
      "line_end": 1140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乒乒乓乓",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1142,
      "line_end": 1142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou_zi",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我连一点礼都没有送，怎么好意思呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1158,
      "line_end": 1158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "用不着，你用不着送礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1160,
      "line_end": 1160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么我用不着送礼?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1162,
      "line_end": 1162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "临时决定的?我听说乡下人成亲大多要准备很久，为什么……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1168,
      "line_end": 1168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么不同?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1174,
      "line_end": 1174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为新郎倌和新娘子都有点特别。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1176,
      "line_end": 1176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么特别?他们究竟是老爷子你的什么人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1178,
      "line_end": 1178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在新郎倌就快出来了，你马上就可以看到他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1180,
      "line_end": 1180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "新郎倌很快就会出来，那么新娘子呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1182,
      "line_end": 1182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "新娘子已经在这屋里了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1184,
      "line_end": 1184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_si_si",
      "speaker_name": "田思思",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这屋里?在哪里?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1186,
      "line_end": 1186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道对面的那位就是新娘子?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
